
LUDO

 - player
  - color (yellow|green|red|blue)
  - pieces (array)
  - startField (field id)
  + setName
  V allPiecesAtHome (true|false)
  V change

 - piece
  - position (field id)
  - count (how far is the piece on the board)
  - cx (integer)
  - cy (integer)
  V moveOrdinary (new field attr)
  V moveFromHome (startField attr)
  V moveFinal (final field attr)
  V goHome (home base field attr)
  V setX (set the cx)
  V setY (set the cy)
  V setPosition (set the position)

 - dice
  - numbers (array)
  + throwDice (integer)

 - diceNumber
  - number (integer)
  - textNumber (name)
